<div class="popBox popBox-quickRecruit">
    <div class="popBox-title tc">我要ta</div>
    <div class="popBox-content">
        <div class="recruit-block clearfix">
            <div class="title fl"><i class="icon-theme"></i>主题</div>
            <div class="block-right fl">
                <div class="invite-theme"><span class="company-name"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;实习生面试邀请</div>
                <div class="invite-jobs clearfix">
                    <div class="jobs-title fl">邀请职位&nbsp;:</div>
                    <div class="jobs fl">
                        <p class='no-job'>您没有可以邀请的有效职位，快去创建一下新职位吧~</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="job-add">
                    <a href="/job/add" target="_blank"><i></i>新建职位</a>
                    <span class="btn-refresh"><i></i>刷新职位</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="recruit-block clearfix">
            <div class="title fl"><i class="icon-text"></i>邀请文</div>
